---
title: Tikka-Style Lamb Burgers with Potato Wedges and Curry Mayo
description: Tonight's meal will transport your tastebuds to warmer climates. These saucy, spicy, fragrant lamb burgers are inspired by Punjabi-style lamb skewers grilled over the fire. Spiced potato wedges and curried mayo provide classic sides with a twist!
